			<h2>
			One comment on &ldquo;Creamy Tomato Pasta with Ham&rdquo;		</h2>
		

		<ol id="comment-list" class="comment-list">
				    <li class="comment even thread-even depth-1" id="li-comment-141740">
	        <div id="comment-141740" class="comment">

            <img alt='' src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%2060%2060'%3E%3C/svg%3E" data-lazy-srcset='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/2f7079857ee314986687eceff9a7fc19590bcd728a0e32c65ce9a01928e23904?s=120&#038;d=blank&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-60 photo' height='60' width='60' data-pin-nopin="true" decoding='async' data-lazy-src="https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/2f7079857ee314986687eceff9a7fc19590bcd728a0e32c65ce9a01928e23904?s=60&#038;d=blank&#038;r=g"/><noscript><img alt='' src='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/2f7079857ee314986687eceff9a7fc19590bcd728a0e32c65ce9a01928e23904?s=60&#038;d=blank&#038;r=g' srcset='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/2f7079857ee314986687eceff9a7fc19590bcd728a0e32c65ce9a01928e23904?s=120&#038;d=blank&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-60 photo' height='60' width='60' data-pin-nopin="true" decoding='async'/></noscript>            
            		
            <div class="post-meta comment-meta">
            	<strong>Ben</strong>            	 &#8212; 
                <time pubdate datetime="2026-05-16T15:23:34-04:00">
                May 16, 2026 @ 3:23 pm                </time>
                
                <a rel="nofollow" class="comment-reply-link" href="#comment-141740" data-commentid="141740" data-postid="35625" data-belowelement="comment-141740" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Ben" aria-label="Reply to Ben">Reply</a>                            </div><!-- .comment-meta -->
			
			<p>I made this and it was delicious, but it was hard to find fat free half and half and I ended up with a bunch left over that quickly went bad. Fat free half and half also seems supiciously fake &#8212; what is the other half, if not fat? Is there anything else to sub? Maybe just skim milk?</p>

	        </div><!-- #comment-## -->
	 
	    </li><!-- #comment-## -->
		</ol><!-- .comment-list -->

				
		<a href="#reply-title" class="smbutton">Leave a comment &raquo;</a>
		
		
		
</div><!-- #comments -->



